Package: MRFraster
Type: Package
Title: Markov random fields as raster objects 
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2012-10-02
Depends: INLA, raster, RandomFields
Enhances: spdep
Author: Patrick Brown <patrick.brown@utoronto.ca>
Maintainer: Patrick Brown <patrick.brown@utoronto.ca>
Description: Simulation and inference of geostatistical and point process data using the Markov random field approximation
to the Matern covariance function.  Data and results are stored as raster objects.
License: GPL
